positories:\r\ndeb http://packages.osrfoundation.org/gazebo/ubuntu trusty main\r\ndeb http://packages.ros.org/ros/ubuntu trusty main\r\n\r\n(This bug is similar to #1187.)", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>ros indigo ubuntu package for rviz (together with dev packages for gazebo 2, 4 and 5) depends on libogre-1.8-dev. libgazebo6-dev depends on libogre-1.9-dev. The only way to install gazebo6-dev or gazebo6-ros packages is therefore to uninstall rviz.</p>\n<p>I use repositories:\ndeb <a href=\"http://packages.osrfoundation.org/gazebo/ubuntu\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">http://packages.osrfoundation.org/gazebo/ubuntu</a> trusty main\ndeb <a href=\"http://packages.ros.org/ros/ubuntu\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">http://packages.ros.org/ros/ubuntu</a> trusty main</p>\n<p>(This bug is similar to <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/1187/libogre-18-dev-dependency-conflict\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"libogre-1.8-dev dependency conflict\" class=\"ap-connect-link\"><s>#1187</s></a>.)</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Jose Luis Rivero", "uuid": "{d12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bd12309b2-f745-42ee-b119-aec4fcdf81fe%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/109284c8b83411dbc7492138f6167e9ed=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsJR-5.png"}}, "nickname": "Jose Luis Rivero", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:155a32e2-420c-4d50-98e0-0e722f63f906"}, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "6.0", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/170782.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2015-08-20T13:45:04.770577+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:45:39.061750+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 1711}